---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout title="Kuzupost PhotoStrips - About">
    <div
        class="relative min-h-[80vh] flex flex-col items-center justify-center py-16 px-4 md:px-6 overflow-hidden bg-neo-pink"
    >
        <!-- Grid Background -->
        <div
            class="absolute inset-0 z-0 pointer-events-none"
            style="background-image: linear-gradient(#111827 4px, transparent 4px), linear-gradient(90deg, #111827 4px, transparent 4px); background-size: 60px 60px; opacity: 0.15;"
        >
        </div>

        <div class="relative z-10 w-full max-w-4xl flex flex-col items-center">
            <h1
                class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-black uppercase text-neo-white bg-neo-black inline-block px-6 py-3 border-4 border-neo-white shadow-[8px_8px_0_0_#ffb6c1] transform -rotate-1 mb-8 hover:rotate-0 transition-transform cursor-pointer"
            >
                <i class="fa fa-users mr-3 text-neo-pink"></i>Tentang Kami
            </h1>

            <div class="w-full space-y-12">
                <!-- Card 1 -->
                <div
                    class="bg-neo-yellow border-[6px] border-neo-black p-8 md:p-12 shadow-[16px_16px_0_0_#111827] transform rotate-2 hover:-rotate-1 hover:-translate-y-2 hover:shadow-[24px_24px_0_0_#111827] transition-all relative"
                >
                    <div
                        class="absolute -top-6 -left-6 w-12 h-12 bg-neo-cyan border-4 border-neo-black rounded-full animate-bounce"
                    >
                    </div>

                    <h2
                        class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-black uppercase mb-6 flex flex-wrap items-center gap-4 text-stroke"
                    >
                        <span class="bg-neo-black text-neo-white p-2"
                            >Siapa</span
                        > Kami?
                    </h2>
                    <p
                        class="text-xl md:text-2xl font-bold leading-relaxed border-l-[12px] border-neo-black pl-6 bg-white/70 p-6 shadow-[8px_8px_0_0_#111827]"
                    >
                        Kuzupost PhotoStrips hadir untuk membawa kenangan klasik
                        gaya photo booth langsung ke browser Anda. Kami percaya
                        bahwa setiap momen pantas dirayakan dengan gaya
                        nostalgia yang seru dan tanpa batas.
                    </p>
                </div>

                <!-- Card 2 -->
                <div
                    class="w-full max-w-4xl bg-neo-white border-4 border-neo-black shadow-[8px_8px_0_0_#111827] p-6 md:p-8 space-y-8 transform -rotate-1 hover:rotate-1 hover:-translate-y-2 hover:shadow-[12px_12px_0_0_#111827] transition-all relative"
                >
                    <h2
                        class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-black uppercase mb-6 text-right w-full block"
                    >
                        Visi <span
                            class="bg-neo-pink text-neo-black p-2 border-4 border-neo-black"
                            >Misi</span
                        >
                    </h2>
                    <p
                        class="text-xl md:text-2xl font-black bg-neo-pink p-3 border-4 border-neo-black shadow-[-4px_4px_0_0_#111827] mb-6 transform rotate-1"
                    >
                        Menjadikan web sebagai tempat interaktif untuk mencetak
                        kenangan. Tidak perlu hardware khusus, cukup senyum ke
                        webcam Anda, hiasi dengan gaya retro, dan simpan
                        hasilnya selamanya.
                    </p>
                </div>

                <div class="flex justify-center mt-12">
                    <button
                        onclick="window.history.back();"
                        class="inline-block bg-neo-black text-neo-white font-black text-lg py-3 px-6 border-4 border-neo-white shadow-[4px_4px_0_0_#111827] hover:shadow-[6px_6px_0_0_#111827] hover:-translate-y-1 active:shadow-none active:translate-y-2 transition-all uppercase tracking-widest"
                    >
                        Hubungi Kami <i class="fa fa-envelope ml-2"></i>
                    </button>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</Layout>
